The paper deals with image analysis and segmentation algorithms, which are typically studied in the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of uncertainty estimation and propagation is also a common topic in data mining (cs.DM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the mention of terabyte-scale analyses suggests that the paper may also be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) research.
